snippet.title: No More Home - Kickstarter Project
snippet.description:
No More Home: A tactical cooperation FPS, fight against giant quadrupeds, and defend your home.

No More Home is a Tactical cooperation FPS, you are part of an elite commando force, came to free the city from the “Salvagers” claw. Terrible extra-terrestrial machines are here to exploit the earth’s resources. Are you just going to run into the fight? Or play stealth and safe?.

Read the full article at: https://gamegeeksnews.com/kickstarter-project-no-more-home/

Back this amazing #KickstarterProject: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/rokyte-studio/no-more-home

#NoMoreHome #KickstarterGame
